Subject: [PATCH 147/242] net: bnx2x: Change variable type to bool
Patch-mainline: v3.13-rc1

Git-commit: b85d717c1b66a40f006148a31e6bbb88ca6b45c0
References: bsc#908684 FATE#317539


The variable rc is only assigned the values true and false.
The function bnx2x_prev_is_path_marked already returns bool.
Change rc type to bool.

The simplified semantic patch that find this problem is as
follows (http://coccinelle.lip6.fr/):

@exists@
type T;
identifier b;
@@
- T
+ bool
  b = ...;
  ... when any
  b = \(true\|false\)

